name: Coming Home (Dylandummy)
description:
You are lost. You are alone. You have no armor. You have no weapons. You have only one thing... You have hope!

Coming Home is just a simple platformer with nothing to hide! Nothing to see here! (Except for a fantastic, semi-easy platform game!) Walk right, read signs, and avoid little grey... are those supposed to be mice?

Created and coded by dylandummy, thumbnail and cover art by @_grace_thi_

Warning: This game features some story elements that could be considered disturbing. This game is not suitable for those who are easily disturbed.
